#

Sweet and Spicy Pickles

15 min
$5
50 kcal
Difficulty: 10%
Servings: 8

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianGluten-FreeLow-Calorie

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Condiment

Tags:

CondimentSnackEasy

Description

A delightful mix of sweetness and heat that adds a zing to any meal!

Ingredients

  • cucumber: 4 large
  • sugar: 1 cup
  • apple cider vinegar: 2 cups
  • red pepper flakes: 1 tablespoon
  • garlic cloves: 4, minced
  • dill weed: 1 tablespoon
  • salt: 1 tablespoon
  • black peppercorns: 1 teaspoon
